nktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5b720966-7eb6-46f2-a00d-0ebfbb7177bc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/59abcfb4d78defab.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"540\", \"originalHeight\" : \"360\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/59abcfb4d78defab.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/59abcfb4d78defab.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"333\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-538bc83a-4897-4a72-9e65-92a560092035\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-57b1fd30-7b8b-47e2-bee5-f955bd7a5506\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c01a73f-9cf8-40e2-960b-ae3d70177bd9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f70ce008-24e2-482e-9352-b9808529bbb6\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de6376d1-4197-4ad7-9012-acc95fff21bb\">이 분들은</span><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c0e8eb8-b2d9-44d9-a5d5-8ef56f7d8b3c\"><b> 드퀘르벵 건초염</b></span><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-165980ba-f7ca-4b2c-85c0-81c570d31cbb\">을 의심해볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b8fbe012-c65d-4c4f-900e-6d9b8a8c1e8b\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e76e4ec9-bc4a-4473-affd-efa575e2306a\">드퀘르벵 건초염은 손목과 엄지손가락의 힘줄이 마찰돼 염증이 생기는 질환입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0a5617f-0a78-43b3-930a-9831f3092a93\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f0a5617f-0a78-43b3-930a-9831f3092a93\", \"src\" : \"https://t1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?fname=http://t1.daumcdn.net/brunch/service/user/4dit/image/tmlV3_9T0AR8MMTqbMP_XmiZYhg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"867\", \"originalHeight\" : \"572\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?fname=http://t1.daumcdn.net/brunch/service/user/4dit/image/tmlV3_9T0AR8MMTqbMP_XmiZYhg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4895e58-165e-4d2b-8aea-0eb5eda4e1e2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4df6855a-2b83-4911-94f7-eda52a6683ae\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-74a8946b-f68c-4022-b90f-dfb252ff1073\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-960bdd19-fa54-4826-80ec-09e824d81911\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-18bf6788-66bd-45a0-8f9a-8c4a8780c9e4\">40-50대에게서 주로 발생하지만, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5063d06d-7003-4b38-99b4-2b3ef7fc5740\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b70f0664-0a8c-4c5a-9014-3f584de6a3df\">스마트폰 사용량이 늘어나면서 젊은 연령층에서도 많이 발생하고 있는데요, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6064a3c9-cefc-472d-8fdc-050c9a6afbb7\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-70d3b76e-240a-4c46-b38e-b0737093e978\">이런 드퀘르벵 건초염을 치료하는 방법은 여러 가지가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1079d664-4055-4c03-9310-051171d7993e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8ad4184-ab23-43bc-a81e-4a05cbefce58\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-db70198c-5988-4597-9f72-7794c7a1274d\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9f62a0dc-6922-47bd-9aeb-c3105a6cd7d5\">서양의학적으로는 물리치료나 주사치료, 수술 등을 시행하지만 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f23e4db-c7a8-46d3-93cb-5eb7b72d70dd\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0293b222-54d2-4fd0-b628-3c74ab4e6ff2\">이런 치료로도 호전되지 않는 경우가 </span><span style=\"color:#0078cb;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e4429622-2a78-4ed0-a6c3-9bd3783492c1\"><b>14∼35%</b></span><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-694a3e27-4b7a-48f0-bc53-320481b50aa9\">에 이른다고 하니 정말 놀랍죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2a1235a6-7755-451c-9eea-dfb3d1b19f64\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2a1235a6-7755-451c-9eea-dfb3d1b19f64\", \"src\" : \"http://chung111.mycafe24.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/%EB%AC%BC%EB%A6%AC%EC%B9%98%EB%A3%8C-102