                   </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-56196a9f-fd24-48f8-b398-3fdcdaccba59\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-56196a9f-fd24-48f8-b398-3fdcdaccba59\", \"src\" : \"https://img.etoday.co.kr/pto_db/2021/10/20211001160908_1671591_1181_788.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1181\", \"originalHeight\" : \"788\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://img.etoday.co.kr/pto_db/2021/10/20211001160908_1671591_1181_788.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fef1437c-80d3-4599-a8a6-b2982fba396b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b799a122-d336-41f6-9719-b79ed09e8353\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de4df455-906a-4866-a402-1adb2a1a530e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-38af96de-1304-4ef2-ab22-8099a71181ee\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-16a9e1c4-9213-4d00-9034-29652d6bfcfb\">최근 국제학술지에 게재된 연구결과에 따르면, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa946150-1305-493f-9176-8716c8535182\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0765cb6-c07c-45c4-acd9-c50fa324530b\">침 치료는 </span><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aeba168d-3dfa-40c3-a0b0-6186869f18ee\"><b>드퀘르벵 건초염</b></span><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1205a09d-6f8d-403d-a898-95f8104b02cb\">에 효과적인 비수술 요법으로 입증되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dbefde09-dbd9-4f61-b455-650bfaf90f29\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-793067c4-8b15-4282-a89f-9dabd0a13f8a\">(‘Phytomedicine’(IF 9.5) ‘드퀘르벵 건초염에 대한 침 치료:무작위 대조시험’)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e343c44e-95c0-4cda-a8a0-95c4cbad0671\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:225px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e343c44e-95c0-4cda-a8a0-95c4cbad0671\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fbe0f8b47af2f97.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"225\", \"originalHeight\" : \"225\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fbe0f8b47af2f97.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4357e38d-c000-46f2-a475-4143d0fc0b6e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8491c0c0-561b-4694-8dcb-9de7430cc0b8\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c2878b8-6940-4cdb-a0cd-6696608ececd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85422ac3-149e-4090-ab36-1f5158a1885e\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a3769600-4b1e-4025-bf63-1102263e37e4\">침 치료는 통증을 줄여주고 팔의 기능과 손의 악력을 개선해줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-28cd081f-692b-4e3b-8609-ff68bdfea50e\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c96cce34-837b-4cf3-b3c0-c5744441eaa9\">또한 2주간의 침 치료로 손목 건초염에 우수한 효과를 보였으며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-01711b23-5cdf-4509-a202-d4e4781486f7\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ec423a28-6cbb-4ee7-ba26-f34256fbc1e3\">12주 후에도 지속됐다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7ea6f4b8-b808-4872-ae09-d6178b232568\"><span style=\"color:#608cba;\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-cb91bb95-35e4-4367-a6c1-6b881f88d729\"><a href=\"https://www.akomnews.com/bbs/board.php?bo_table&#x3D;news&amp;wr_id&#x3D;51481\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><u>https://www.akomnews.com/bbs/board.php?bo_table&#x3D;news&amp;wr_id&#x3D;51481</u></a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-image\" id=\"SE-9208f3e7-c5ac-46be-bef5-8ae5d09fe713\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-image se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://www.akomnews.com/bbs/board.php?bo_table&#x3D;news&amp;wr_id&#x3D;51481\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akomnews.com%2Fdata%2Ffile%2Fnews%2Fthumb%2Fthumb-51481-560x240.jpg%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://www.akomnews.com/bbs/board.php?bo_table&#x3D;news&amp;wr_id&#x3D;51481\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">손목 드퀘르벵 건초염의 침 치료 효과 ‘입증’</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">무처치군 VAS는 평균 3.4mm 감소한 반면 침 치료군은 19.5mm 감소국제학술지 ‘Phytomedicine’ 연구결과 게재…12주 후에도 개선효과 지속</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">www.akomnews.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-9208f3e7-c5ac-46be-bef5-8ae5d09fe713\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://www.akomnews.com/bbs/board.php?bo_table&#x3D;news&amp;wr_id&#x3D;51481\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akomnews.com%2Fdata%2Ffile%2Fnews%2Fthumb%2Fthumb-51481-560x240.jpg%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e4c61ca7-09c8-49d5-9c0f-f35520162fae\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a82de0f1-25d9-4890-87fc-6eca42b1c59c\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3620db5d-d1b8-4bc9-8a9b-16d2c12d5260\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a052de41-3c3e-4115-88c4-e6660cfcf3e5\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d509ed8d-46e7-4834-9150-9c1ebfba4bd9\">침 치료 시 사용하는 혈위는 LI-5 (陽溪), LU-7 (列缺), LU-9 (太淵), 아시혈 등이지만 만성 건초염일 경우 도침 치료를 병행하면 더 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-74b45d56-7264-43e7-ba62-fd44de44349f\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b54eb93e-5f02-4eb1-8e05-7b41a500bc38\">도침은 힘줄 주변의 섬유화와 유착을 해소해줍니다.</span></p><